  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca - \u0db8\u0ddb\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dad\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith - Maithri in a crucial meeting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special meeting chaired by former President Maithripala Sirisena and Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa was held today (04th) at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo.",
        "Arrangements were made for this discussion to be held as a crucial meeting of the 'National Reforms and Progress' program to rebuild the country, which has seriously collapsed.",
        "The discussion was attended by CV Wigneswaran, P. Digambaram, Samagi Jana Balavega General Secretary Ranjith Maddumabandara, Samagi Jana Balavega MP Rajitha Senaratne were present.",
        "In addition, a group of civil activists including Victor Ivan, Janaranjana, Gamini Viangoda were also present."
      ],
